'''美國人'''指的是[[美國公民|美國公民]]。[[僑民|僑民]]或[[美國永久居民|美國永久居民]]也可申請[[美國|美國]]國籍。<ref name="nationals and citizens">{{USC|8|1401}}; {{USC|8|1408}}; {{USC|8|1452}}; see also
*{{cite web |url=https://casetext.com/case/ricketts-v-attorney-gen-united-states#p494 |title=Ricketts v. Attorney General, 897 F.3d 491 |page=494 n.3 |date=2018-07-30 |work=Third Circuit |quote=While all citizens are nationals, not all nationals are citizens. |access-date=2021-09-06 |archive-date=2021-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210812103920/https://casetext.com/case/ricketts-v-attorney-gen-united-states#p494 |dead-url=no }}
*{{cite web |url=https://cite.case.law/f3d/788/300/4230126/#p302 |title=Tuaua v. United States, 788 F.3d 300 |page=302 |date=2015-06-05 |work=D.C. Circuit |access-date=2021-09-06 |archive-date=2021-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112052306/https://cite.case.law/f3d/788/300/4230126/#p302 |dead-url=no }}
*{{cite web |url=https://cite.case.law/f3d/502/337/#p341 |title=Fernandez v. Keisler, 502 F.3d 337 |page=341 |date=2007-09-26 |work=Fourth Circuit |quote=All citizens of the United States are nationals, but some nationals are not citizens. |access-date=2021-09-06 |archive-date=2021-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210830214914/https://cite.case.law/f3d/502/337/#p341 |dead-url=no }}
