美國是一個[[多元文化主義|多元文化主義]]國家。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/population/pop-profile/2000/chap16.pdf |title=Our Diverse Population: Race and Hispanic Origin, 2000 |access-date=2008-04-24 |publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]] |archive-date=2004-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040715050055/https://www.census.gov/population/pop-profile/2000/chap16.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[美國普查局|美國普查局]]因統計需要將美國人劃分為六個種族：白人、美國印第安人和阿拉斯加原住民、亞洲人、黑人或非洲裔美國人、[[夏威夷原住民|夏威夷原住民]]和其他太平洋島原住民，以及兩個或兩個以上種族的人。此外也可以選擇「其他種族」。普查局還將美國人分為拉丁裔和非拉丁裔，而拉丁裔是美國最大的少數族裔。<ref name="Standards">{{cite web|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/omb/fedreg/1997standards.html |title=Revisions to the Standards for the Classification of Federal Data on Race and Ethnicity |access-date=2008-05-05 |publisher=[[Office_of_Management_and_Budget|Office of Management and Budget]] |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090315191301/https://www.whitehouse.gov/omb/fedreg/1997standards.html |archive-date=2009-03-15 }}</ref><ref name="Overview">{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/prod/2001pubs/cenbr01-1.pdf |title=Overview of Race and Hispanic Origin: 2000 |access-date=2015-01-02 |last=Grieco |first=Elizabeth M |author2=Rachel C. Cassidy |publisher=[[United_States_Census_Bureau|United States Census Bureau]] |archive-date=2019-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501024010/https://www.census.gov/prod/2001pubs/cenbr01-1.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=PEPT3race08>{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov |title=U.S. Census website |work=2008 Population Estimates |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |access-date=2010-02-28 |archive-date=1996-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/19961227012639/https://www.census.gov/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===美國白人===
{{main|美國白人|歐裔美國人}}
根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，3.08億美國人中有72.4%是白人。<ref name="TWP2010">{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-05.pdf |title=The White Population: 2010 |author=Lindsay Hixson |author2=Bradford B. Hepler |author3=Myoung Ouk Kim |date=September 2011 |work=United States Census Bureau |publisher=United States Department of Commerce |access-date=2012-11-20 |archive-date=2011-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930074513/https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-05.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>其祖先是歐洲、中東和北非的原住民。<ref name=c2010 />另有2.4%是白人與其他種族的混血兒，其中黑白混血兒最多。<ref name="TWP2010" />拉丁裔白人佔美國人口的9.4%，在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞]]、[[德克薩斯|德克薩斯]]、[[新墨西哥|新墨西哥]]、[[內華達|內華達]]和[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]佔多數。<ref>{{cite web|title=U.S. whites will soon be the minority in number, but not power – Baltimore Sun|periodical=[[The_Baltimore_Sun|The Baltimore Sun]]|url=http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/opinion/oped/bs-ed-op-0809-minority-majority-20170808-story.html|access-date=2018-01-21|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808200616/http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/opinion/oped/bs-ed-op-0809-minority-majority-20170808-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8902484 |title=Minority population surging in Texas |date=2005-08-18 |work=NBC News |agency=Associated Press |access-date=2009-12-07 |archive-date=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231232030/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8902484/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[非拉丁裔白人|非拉丁裔白人]]比例最高的州是[[緬因州|緬因州]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/newsroom/releases/archives/population/cb12-90.html |title=Most Children Younger Than Age 1 are Minorities, Census Bureau Reports |last1=Bernstein |first1=Robert |date=2012-05-17 |work=United States Census Bureau |publisher=United States Department of Commerce |access-date=2012-12-16 |archive-date=2012-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120518211419/https://www.census.gov/newsroom/releases/archives/population/cb12-90.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，非白人在[[哥倫比亞特區|哥倫比亞特區]]和五個有常住人口的海外領土佔多數。<ref name=c2010 />

最早在美國大陸建立殖民據點的歐洲人是[[西班牙人|西班牙人]]，這段歷史可以追溯到1565年。<ref name=loc>{{cite web |url=http://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/colonial/jb_colonial_augustin_1.html |title=A Spanish Expedition Established St. Augustine in Florida |publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]] |access-date=2009-03-27 |archive-date=2018-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181010022552/http://www.americaslibrary.gov/jb/colonial/jb_colonial_augustin_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{link-en|馬丁·德·阿圭列斯|Martín de Argüelles}}是第一個生於美洲大陸的歐洲裔，他生於1566年[[新西班牙總督轄區|新西班牙總督轄區]]的[[聖奧古斯丁_(佛羅里達州)|聖奧古斯丁]]。<ref>{{cite book|author=D. H. Figueredo|title=Latino Chronology: Chronologies of the American Mosaic|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TWX5d27NkFgC&pg=PT35|year=2007|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-313-34154-0|page=35|access-date=2021-09-18|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811011124/https://books.google.com/books?id=TWX5d27NkFgC&pg=PT35|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，西班牙人還於1521年在波多黎各建立了[[聖胡安_(波多黎各)|聖胡安市]]。[[弗吉尼亚·戴尔|弗吉尼亚·戴尔]]是第一個生於北美十三州的英格蘭裔，她生於1587年的[[羅阿諾克殖民地|羅阿諾克殖民地]]。

根據2017年{{link-en|美國社區調查|American Community Survey}}，[[德裔美國人|德裔]]、[[愛爾蘭裔美國人|愛爾蘭裔]]、[[英格蘭裔美國人|英格蘭裔]]和[[意大利裔美國人|意大利裔]]是美國的四大歐裔群體，佔總人口的35.1%。<ref name="2017 ACS">{{cite web |url=https://factfinder.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=ACS_14_1YR_DP02&prodType=table |title=Selected Social Characteristics in the United States (DP02): 2017 American Community Survey 1-Year Estimates |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau |access-date=2018-11-20 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200214010640/https://factfinder.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=ACS_14_1YR_DP02&prodType=table |archive-date=2020-02-14 |url-status=dead }}</ref>然而，英格蘭裔和[[英國裔美國人|英國裔]]的人口被認為遭到嚴重低估。因為他們在美國居住的時間很長，一般只會說自己是{{link-en|美國祖先|American ancestry|美國人}}，而不會強調自己的祖先來自哪裏。{{noteTag|1=自1990年起，美國人口普查的族群認同一欄中增加了「美國人」這一選項。}}這一現像在長期以英國裔為主的[[上南方|上南方]]尤其明顯。<ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=mCopDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA200 Ethnic Landscapes of America] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=mCopDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA200 |date=20220315064639 }} - By John A. Cross</ref><ref>[https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=sQOJDBgBFmYC&pg=PA6 Census and you: monthly news from the U.S. Bureau... Volume 28, Issue 2] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=sQOJDBgBFmYC&pg=PA6 |date=20220315064640 }} - By United States. Bureau of the Census</ref><ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=SVoAXh-dNuYC&pg=PA57 Sharing the Dream: White Males in a Multicultural America] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SVoAXh-dNuYC&pg=PA57 |date=20150907093623 }} By Dominic J. Pulera.</ref><ref>Reynolds Farley, 'The New Census Question about Ancestry: What Did It Tell Us?', ''Demography'', Vol. 28, No. 3 (August 1991), pp. 414, 421.</ref><ref>Stanley Lieberson and Lawrence Santi, 'The Use of Nativity Data to Estimate Ethnic Characteristics and Patterns', ''Social Science Research'', Vol. 14, No. 1 (1985), pp. 44-6.</ref><ref>Stanley Lieberson and Mary C. Waters, 'Ethnic Groups in Flux: The Changing Ethnic Responses of American Whites', ''Annals of the American Academy of Political and Social Science'', Vol. 487, No. 79 (September 1986), pp. 82-86.</ref>

在美國所有種族中，歐裔美國人的[[美國貧困問題|貧困率]]最低，[[美國教育|受教育程度]]、{{link-en|美國的家庭所得|Household income in the United States|家庭所得}}中位數和{{link-en|美國個人所得|Personal income in the United States|個人所得}}中位數位居第二。<ref name="Poverty rate">{{cite web
|url=https://www.census.gov/prod/2005pubs/p60-229.pdf
|title=Income, Poverty, and Health Insurance Coverage in the United States: 2004
|access-date=2021-09-18
|archive-date=2022-01-23
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123124431/https://www.census.gov/prod/2005pubs/p60-229.pdf
|dead-url=no
}}</ref><ref name="Median household income newsbrief, US Census Bureau 2005">{{cite web|url=https://www.census.gov/Press-Release/www/releases/archives/income_wealth/005647.html |title=Median household income newsbrief, US Census Bureau 2005 |access-date=2006-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060903121511/http://www.census.gov/Press-Release/www/releases/archives/income_wealth/005647.html |archive-date=2006-09-03 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name="US Census Bureau, Personal income for Asian Americans, age 25+, 2006">{{cite web|url=http://pubdb3.census.gov/macro/032006/perinc/new03_008.htm |title=US Census Bureau, Personal income for Asian Americans, age 25+, 2006 |access-date=2006-12-17 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060929074108/http://pubdb3.census.gov/macro/032006/perinc/new03_008.htm |archive-date=2006-09-29 }}</ref>

