===非裔美國人===
{{main|非裔美國人}}

非裔美國人通常來自[[撒哈拉以南非洲|撒哈拉以南非洲]]和[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]。<ref name="IOM">{{cite web|title=Race, Ethnicity, and Language data - Standardization for Health Care Quality Improvement|url=http://www.ahrq.gov/sites/default/files/publications/files/iomracereport.pdf|publisher=Institute of Medicine of the National Academies|access-date=May 10, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129053700/https://www.ahrq.gov/sites/default/files/publications/files/iomracereport.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="2010USCBAA" />不過並非所有來自撒哈拉以南非洲的人都是黑人，許多[[佛得角|佛得角]]裔、[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]]裔、[[阿非利卡人|阿非利卡人]]，以及來自[[东非|东非]]和[[萨赫勒|萨赫勒]]地區的居民並非黑人。<ref name="IOM"/>

根據2009年美國社區調查，全美共有38,093,725名非裔美國人，佔總人口的12.4%。其中37,144,530名為非拉丁裔黑人，佔總人口的12.1%。<ref name="factfinder.census.gov">[http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/ADPTable?_bm=y&-geo_id=01000US&-qr_name=ACS_2009_1YR_G00_DP5&-ds_name=&-_lang=en&-redoLog=false&-format= United States – ACS Demographic and Housing Estimates: 2009] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20200211182353/http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/ADPTable?_bm=y&-geo_id=01000US&-qr_name=ACS_2009_1YR_G00_DP5&-ds_name=&-_lang=en&-redoLog=false&-format= |date=February 11, 2020 }}. Factfinder.census.gov. Retrieved December 9, 2010.</ref>根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，非裔美國人（包括混血黑人）共有4200萬，<ref name="2010USCBAA">{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-06.pdf |title=The Black Population: 2010 |author=Sonya Tastogi |author2=Tallese D. Johnson |author3=Elizabeth M. Hoeffel |author4=Malcolm P. Drewery, Jr. |date=September 2011 |work=United States Census Bureau |publisher=United States Department of Commerce |access-date=September 11, 2012 |archive-date=2019-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190131170100/https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-06.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>佔總人口的14%。<ref name="NRC201029SEP11">{{cite web |url=http://2010.census.gov/news/releases/operations/cb11-cn185.html |title=2010 Census Shows Black Population has Highest Concentration in the South |date=September 29, 2011 |work=United States Census Bureau |publisher=United States Department of Commerce |access-date=September 11, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120915180008/http://2010.census.gov/news/releases/operations/cb11-cn185.html |archive-date=September 15, 2012 |url-status=dead}}</ref>非裔美國人主要生活在[[美國南部|美國南部]]（55%） 。與2000年相比，[[美國東北部|美國東北部]]與[[美國中西部|中西部]]的黑人數量有所下降。<ref name="NRC201029SEP11" />

大部分非裔美國人的祖先都是來自[[西非|西非]]的俘虜，他們被當做[[美國奴隸制度|奴隸]]帶到美國。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mumford1.dyndns.org/cen2000/BlackWhite/BlackDiversityReport/black-diversity03.htm |title=The size and regional distribution of the black population |access-date=October 1, 2007 |publisher=Lewis Mumford Center |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012170004/http://mumford1.dyndns.org/cen2000/BlackWhite/BlackDiversityReport/black-diversity03.htm |archive-date=October 12, 2007 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>1619年，維吉尼亞州的[[詹姆斯敦_(維吉尼亞州)|詹姆斯敦]]首次僱傭黑奴。英國人將這些奴隸視為[[契约劳工|契约劳工]]，工作滿一定年數便可獲得自由。隨著時間的推移，這種做法逐漸被[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]基於種族的奴隸制-{}-取代。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/aia/part1/1narr2.html|title=New World Exploration and English Ambition |work=The Terrible Transformation |publisher=PBS |access-date=September 11, 2011 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20070614105621/http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/aia/part1/1narr2.html| archive-date= June 14, 2007 | url-status= live}}</ref>所有[[十三殖民地|美國殖民地]]都有奴隶制，北方黑人通常是僕人，南方黑人通常是種植園勞工。<ref>{{cite book |title=Exchanging Our Country Marks: The Transformation of African Identities in the Colonial and Antebellum South |last=Gomez |first=Michael A. |year=1998 |publisher=University of North Carolina Press |isbn=9780807846940 |pages=384 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tfHU4mOPMmMC |access-date=2021-11-27 |archive-date=2021-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211127134709/https://books.google.com/books?id=tfHU4mOPMmMC |dead-url=no }}</ref>獨立戰爭時期，一些黑人在[[大陆军|大陆军]]或{{link-en|大陸海軍|Continental Navy}}中服役。<ref>{{link-en|Liberty!}} (Documentary) Episode II:''Blows Must Decide: 1774-1776''. ©1997 {{link-en|Twin Cities Public Television, Inc.}} {{ISBN|1-4157-0217-9}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Blacks in the American Revolution |series=Volume 55 of Contributions in American history |last=Foner |first=Philip Sheldon |year=1976 |publisher=Greenwood Press |isbn=9780837189468 |page=70 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Wk92AAAAMAAJ&q=Philip+S.+Foner+Blacks+in+the+Revolution |access-date=2021-11-27 |archive-date=2021-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211127134709/https://books.google.com/books?id=Wk92AAAAMAAJ&q=Philip+S.+Foner+Blacks+in+the+Revolution |dead-url=no }}</ref>也有些黑人是{{link-en|黑人效忠派|Black Loyalist|保王黨}}，在[[大英帝國|英軍]]服役。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/pathways/blackhistory/work_community/loyalists.htm |title=Black Loyalists |work=Black Presence |publisher=The National Archives |access-date=September 11, 2012 |archive-date=2021-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210825194326/https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/pathways/blackhistory/work_community/loyalists.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>1804年，美國[[梅森-迪克森線|梅森-迪克森線]]以北的州{{link-en|美國的廢奴主義|Abolitionism in the United States|廢除了奴隸制}}，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pbs.org/wnet/slavery/experience/freedom/history.html |title=Freedom & Emancipation |author=Nicholas Boston |author2=Jennifer Hallam |year=2004 |work=Educational Broadcasting Corporation |publisher=Public Broadcasting Service |access-date=September 11, 2012 |archive-date=2017-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025150351/http://www.pbs.org/wnet/slavery/experience/freedom/history.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>而[[美國南部|南方各州]]仍保留奴隸制。雙方矛盾的激化最終導致了[[南北战争|南北战争]]。最終，北方軍獲得勝利，[[美利坚合众国宪法第十三条修正案|宪法第十三条修正案]]獲得通過，奴隸制正式廢除。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ourdocuments.gov/doc.php?flash=true&doc=40 |title=13th Amendment to the U.S. Constitution |work=ourdocuments.gov |publisher=National Archives and Records Administration |access-date=September 11, 2012 |archive-date=2022-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220106092345/https://www.ourdocuments.gov/doc.php?flash=true&doc=40 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[美國重建時期|美國重建時期]]結束後，{{link-en|非裔美國人首次在國會取得席位|List of African-American officeholders during the Reconstruction}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://baic.house.gov/historical-essays/essay.html?intID=3 |title=The Fifteenth Amendment in Flesh and Blood |work=Office of the Clerk |publisher=United States House of Representatives |access-date=September 11, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121211224758/http://baic.house.gov/historical-essays/essay.html?intID=3 |archive-date=December 11, 2012 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>但他們仍然沒有[[选举权|选举权]]，並依照[[吉姆·克勞法|吉姆·克勞法]]與白人[[種族隔離|強制隔離]]。<ref>{{cite book |title=American Black History |last=Walter |first=Hazen |year=2004 |publisher=Lorenz Educational Press |isbn=9780787706036 |page=37 |access-date=September 11, 2012 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GuvsptYLFL4C&q=Jim%20Crow%20Laws%20Reconstruction%20African%20Americans&pg=PA37 |archive-date=2021-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211127134709/https://books.google.com/books?id=GuvsptYLFL4C&q=Jim%20Crow%20Laws%20Reconstruction%20African%20Americans&pg=PA37 |dead-url=no }}</ref>這種情況一直持續至1960年代的[[非裔美國人民權運動|非裔美國人民權運動]]時期，在非裔美國人的持續抗爭下，[[選舉法案_(1965年)|選舉法案]]和[[1964年民權法案|1964年民權法案]]得到通過，種族間的權利不平等得到解決。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nps.gov/nr/travel/civilrights/prize.htm |title=The Prize |work=We Shall Overcome |publisher=National Park Service |access-date=September 11, 2012 |archive-date=2021-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606141656/https://www.nps.gov/nr/travel/civilrights/prize.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

根據2000年的普查數據，相較於非裔美國人這一身份，絕大多數{{link-en|非洲移民|African immigration to the United States}}更認同自身的原生民族，僅有5%的非洲移民認為自己是非裔美國人。其中西非移民對非裔美國人的認同度最高（4%-9%），維德角、東非和非洲南部的移民認同度最低（0%-4%）。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kusow|first1=AM|title=African Immigrants in the United States: Implications for Affirmative Action|url=http://lib.dr.iastate.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1005&context=soc_las_pubs|publisher=Iowa State University|access-date=May 10, 2016|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610034339/http://lib.dr.iastate.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1005&context=soc_las_pubs|dead-url=no}}</ref>

