===美洲原住民===
{{See also|印第安事務局}}
根據2010年人口普查，美國有520萬人（佔總人口1.7%）有原住民血統，其中230萬是混血。40.7%的原住民居住在[[美國西部|美國西部]]。<ref name="2010CensusAIAN">{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-10.pdf |title=The American Indian and Alaska Native Population: 2010 |author=Tina Norris |author2=Paula L. Vines |author3=Elizabeth M. Hoeffel |date=January 2012 |work=United States Census Bureau |publisher=United States Department of Commerce |access-date=2012-09-09 |archive-date=2012-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505221036/http://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-10.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>其他種族也不同程度地含有{{link-en|美國原住民祖先|Native American ancestry|原住民的基因}}，[[美國黑人|美國黑人]]平均含有0.8%的原住民基因，[[歐裔美國人|白人]]有0.18%，而[[拉丁裔美國人|拉丁裔]]則有18.0%。<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Bryc |first1=Katarzyna |last2=Durand |first2=Eric Y. |last3=Macpherson |first3=J. Michael |last4=Reich |first4=David |last5=Mountain |first5=Joanna L. |date=January 2015 |title=The Genetic Ancestry of African Americans, Latinos, and European Americans across the United States |journal=The American Journal of Human Genetics |volume=96 |issue=1 |pages=37–53 |doi=10.1016/j.ajhg.2014.11.010 |pmid=25529636 |pmc=4289685 |issn=0002-9297}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Carl Zimmer |title=White? Black? A Murky Distinction Grows Still Murkier |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/25/science/23andme-genetic-ethnicity-study.html |access-date=2018-10-21 |work=The New York Times |date=2014-12-24 |quote=The researchers found that European-Americans had genomes that were on average 98.6 percent European, .19 percent African, and .18 Native American. |archive-date=2020-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115003450/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/25/science/23andme-genetic-ethnicity-study.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

美洲原住民於45,000至10,000年前[[遷徙新大陸模型|來到]][[美洲|美洲]]大陸。<ref>{{cite book |title=The Complete Idiot's Guide to American History |series=Complete Idiot's Guide to |last=Axelrod |first=Alan |year=2003 |publisher=Penguin |isbn=9780028644646 |page=4 |access-date=2012-09-09 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=O4w2Vb2JzFUC&q=Chukchi%20people%20first%20americans&pg=PA4 |archive-date=2021-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210813011654/https://books.google.com/books?id=O4w2Vb2JzFUC&q=Chukchi%20people%20first%20americans&pg=PA4 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[前哥倫布時期|前哥倫布時期]]的原住民發展出了數百種不同文化。<ref>{{cite book |title=Chronology of Americans and the Environment |last=Magoc |first=Chris J. |year=2011 |publisher=ABC-CLIO |isbn=9781598844115 |page=1 |access-date=2012-09-09 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BA_L6AyjsfUC&q=Paleoamericans%20migration&pg=PA1 |archive-date=2021-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210812174307/https://books.google.com/books?id=BA_L6AyjsfUC&q=Paleoamericans%20migration&pg=PA1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>隨著{{link-en|哥倫布的航行|Voyages of Christopher Columbus|哥倫布的到來}}<ref>{{cite book |title=The Diario of Christopher Columbus's First Voyage to America, 1492-1493 |series=Volume 70 of American Exploration and Travel Series |last1=Columbus |first1=Christopher |author-link=Christopher Columbus |last2=de las Casas |first2=Bartolomé |last3=Dunn |first3=Oliver |last4=Kelley |first4=James Edward |editor1-first=Bartolomé |editor1-last=de las Casas |editor2-first=Oliver |editor2-last=Dunn |year=1991 |publisher=University of Oklahoma Press |isbn=9780806123844 |pages=491 |access-date=2012-09-09 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nS6kRnXJgCEC |archive-date=2021-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112054810/https://books.google.com/books?id=nS6kRnXJgCEC |dead-url=no }}</ref>，歐洲開始[[美洲殖民|殖民美洲]]。從16世紀到19世紀，{{link-en|美國原住民人口史|Population history of indigenous peoples of the Americas|原住民不斷減少}}。其中的原因包括歐洲人與原住民之間的[[印第安戰爭|戰爭]]和[[異族通婚|通婚]]<ref>{{cite book |title=One Nation, One Blood: Interracial Marriage In American Fiction, Scandal, and Law, 1820-1870 |last=Woods Weierman |first=Karen |year=2005 |publisher=University of Massachusetts Press |isbn=9781558494831 |page=44 |access-date=2012-09-09 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=24mIQuLBuN8C&q=Native%20American%20intermarriage&pg=PA44 |archive-date=2021-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210812174308/https://books.google.com/books?id=24mIQuLBuN8C&q=Native%20American%20intermarriage&pg=PA44 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mann |first1=Kaarin |year=2007 |title=Interracial Marriage In Early America: Motivation and the Colonial Project |journal=Michigan Journal of History |issue=Fall |publisher=University of Michigan |url=http://www.umich.edu/~historyj/docs/2007-fall/Interracial_Marriage_in_Early_America_Mann.pdf |access-date=2012-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515063053/http://www.umich.edu/~historyj/docs/2007-fall/Interracial_Marriage_in_Early_America_Mann.pdf |archive-date=2013-05-15 |url-status=dead }}</ref>，對原住民的[[奴役|奴役]]、強制遷移<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pbs.org/kera/usmexicanwar/prelude/md_native_american_displacement.html |title=Native American Displacement Amid U.S. Expansion |author=R. David Edmunds |date=2006-03-14 |work=KERA |publisher=Public Broadcasting Service |access-date=2012-09-09 |archive-date=2019-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191102184426/http://www.pbs.org/kera/usmexicanwar/prelude/md_native_american_displacement.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[种族灭绝|种族灭绝]]<ref>{{cite book |title=American Indian Holocaust and Survival: A Population History Since 1492 |series=Volume 186 of Civilization of the American Indian Series |last=Thornton |first=Russell |year=1987 |publisher=University of Oklahoma Press |isbn=9780806122205 |page=[https://archive.org/details/americanindianho00thor_0/page/49 49] |access-date=2012-09-09 |url=https://archive.org/details/americanindianho00thor_0 |quote=genocide warfare europeans american indians. }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title=Encyclopedia Of Native American Wars And Warfare |series=Facts on File library of American History |last1=Kessel |first1=William B. |last2=Wooster |first2=Robert |year=2005 |publisher=Infobase Publishing |isbn=9780816033379 |pages=398 |access-date=2012-09-09 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=laxSyAp89G4C |archive-date=2021-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903092537/https://books.google.com/books?id=laxSyAp89G4C |dead-url=no }}</ref>，還有歐洲人帶來的[[流行病|流行病]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bianchine |first1=Peter J. |last2=Russo |first2=Thomas A. |year=1992 |title=The Role of Epidemic Infectious Diseases in the Discovery of America |journal=Allergy and Asthma Proceedings |volume=13 |issue=5 |pages=225–232 |publisher=OceanSide Publications, Inc |doi=10.2500/108854192778817040 |pmid=1483570}}</ref>

