===多種族美國人===
隨著時代變遷，美國的多種族運動也逐漸壯大。<ref>{{cite book|author=Jon M. Spencer|title=The New Colored People: The Mixed-Race Movement in America|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zq4UCgAAQBAJ&pg=PR1|date=August 2000|publisher=NYU Press|isbn=978-0-8147-8072-5|access-date=2021-09-27|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053327/https://books.google.com/books?id=zq4UCgAAQBAJ&pg=PR1|dead-url=no}}<br />{{cite book|author1=Loretta I. Winters|author2=Herman L. DeBose|title=New Faces in a Changing America: Multiracial Identity in the 21st Century|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=beNY-_ooPWoC&pg=PP1|year=2003|publisher=SAGE|isbn=978-0-7619-2300-8|access-date=2021-09-27|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053332/https://books.google.com/books?id=beNY-_ooPWoC&pg=PP1|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年，[[混血兒|多種族]]美國人有700萬，佔總人口的2.3%；<ref name=b02001/>而根據2010年的普查，這一數字增長到了9,009,073，佔總人口的2.9%。其中[[黑白混血兒|黑白混血兒]]最常見，有1,834,212名，<ref name="kHnJrR2011">{{cite web |url=https://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-02.pdf |title=Overview of Race and Hispanic Origin: 2010 |author=Karen R. Humes |author2=Nicholas A. Jones |author3=Roberto R. Ramirez |date=March 2011 |work=2010 Census Briefs |publisher=United States Census Bureau |access-date=2013-02-22 |archive-date=2011-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429214029/http://www.census.gov/prod/cen2010/briefs/c2010br-02.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>第44任美國總統[[巴拉克·歐巴馬|巴拉克·歐巴馬]]就是其中一例。他的母親是白人（有英格蘭和愛爾蘭血統），而父親則是生於[[肯亞|肯亞]]的[[盧歐族|盧歐族]]<ref>{{cite news |author1=Ewen MacAskill |author2=Nicholas Watt |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2011/may/20/obama-irish-roots-european-tour |title=Obama looks forward to rediscovering his Irish roots on European tour |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=2011-05-20 |access-date=2011-08-03 |archive-date=2021-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112054825/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2011/may/20/obama-irish-roots-european-tour |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Mason |first=Jeff |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-obama-ireland-idUSTRE74M09F20110523 |title=Obama visits family roots in Ireland |work=Reuters |date=2011-05-23 |access-date=2011-08-03 |archive-date=2021-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112054832/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-obama-ireland-idUSTRE74M09F20110523 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（但自我認同為非裔美國人）。<ref>{{cite news |title=Obama's census-form choice: 'Black' |author=Oscar Avila |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/apr/04/nation/la-na-obama-census4-2010apr04 |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=2010-04-04 |access-date=2013-02-22 |archive-date=2013-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524142628/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/apr/04/nation/la-na-obama-census4-2010apr04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Asked to Declare His Race, Obama Checks 'Black' |author=Sam Roberts |author2=Peter Baker |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/03/us/politics/03census.html?_r=0 |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2010-04-02 |access-date=2013-02-22 |archive-date=2021-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053412/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/03/us/politics/03census.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

