==文化==
{{Main|美國文化}}
[[File:Motherhood_and_apple_pie.jpg|thumb]]和[[棒球|棒球]]是美國文化的象徵]]
美國地域寬廣，人口眾多，文化多樣性高。[[保守主義|保守主義]]與[[自由主義|自由主義]]，科學與宗教在這裏碰撞融合。美國人普遍崇尚[[個人主義|個人主義]]，相信自由、[[平等主義|平等]]與[[民主|民主]]的價值，對[[言論自由|言論自由]]與國家的政治制度十分重視。此外，美國人也比較喜歡冒險。

[[美國文化|美國文化]]主要被[[西方文化|西方文化]]所影響，但也受到了[[美國原住民|原住民]]、[[非裔美國人|西非]]、[[亞裔美國人|東亞]]、[[玻里尼西亞|玻里尼西亞]]和[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]文化的影響。{{link-en|美國殖民史|Colonial history of the United States|殖民時期}}對美國影響最大的是英國。通過殖民，英國向美洲大陸傳播了他們的[[英語|語言]]、[[英格蘭法律制度|法律]]與[[英國文化|其他文化]]。<ref>{{cite book|author=Carlos E. Cortés|title=Multicultural America: A Multimedia Encyclopedia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VQ1zAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA220|date=2013-09-03|publisher=SAGE Publications|isbn=978-1-4522-7626-7|page=220|quote=The dominance of English and Anglo values in U.S. culture is evident in the country's major institutions, demonstrating the melting pot model.|access-date=2021-09-20|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112054948/https://books.google.com/books?id=VQ1zAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA220|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，以[[德國文化|德國]]、<ref name=kirschbaum>{{cite book|last=Kirschbaum|first=Erik|title=The eradication of German culture in the United States, 1917-1918|year=1986|publisher=H.-D. Heinz|isbn=3-88099-617-2|page=155|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JvUMAQAAMAAJ|access-date=2021-09-20|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053618/https://books.google.com/books?id=JvUMAQAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[法國文化|法國]]<ref>{{cite book|author=Peter J. Parish|title=Reader's Guide to American History|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DnQTAXf4NuIC&pg=PA276|date=January 1997|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-884964-22-0|page=276|quote=However, France was second only to Britain in its influence upon the formation of American politics and culture.|access-date=2021-09-20|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053616/https://books.google.com/books?id=DnQTAXf4NuIC&pg=PA276|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[義大利文化|義大利]]<ref>{{cite book|author1=Marilyn J. Coleman|author2=Lawrence H. Ganong|title=The Social History of the American Family: An Encyclopedia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=R3VpBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA775|date=2014-09-16|publisher=SAGE Publications|isbn=978-1-4522-8615-0|page=775|quote=As the communities grew and prospered, Italian food, entertainment, and music influenced American life and culture.|access-date=2021-09-20|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053722/https://books.google.com/books?id=R3VpBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA775|dead-url=no}}</ref>為代表的其他一些歐洲國家也對美國文化產生了重要影響。

美國的本土文化也有著強大的影響力。[[美國節日|美國的本土節日]]、[[美國體育|體育運動]]、{{link-en|軍事傳統|Military tradition}}<ref>{{cite book|author1=M. D. R. Evans|author2=Jonathan Kelley|title=Religion, Morality and Public Policy in International Perspective, 1984-2002|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QwuLhMDUKdkC&pg=PA302|date=January 2004|publisher=Federation Press|isbn=978-1-86287-451-0|page=302|access-date=2021-09-20|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112053725/https://books.google.com/books?id=QwuLhMDUKdkC&pg=PA302|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及藝術和娛樂方面的創新帶給國民強烈的[[民族主義|民族自豪感]]。<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |agency=Associated Press |date=2006-06-27 |title=America tops in national pride survey finds |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/13577802/ns/us_news-life/t/america-tops-national-pride-survey-finds/#.VEiGMyLF-8A |newspaper=NBC News |access-date=2014-10-22 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923115558/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/13577802/ns/us_news-life/t/america-tops-national-pride-survey-finds/#.VEiGMyLF-8A |dead-url=no }}<br />{{cite book|author=Elizabeth Theiss-Morse|author-link=Elizabeth Theiss-Morse|title=Who Counts as an American?: The Boundaries of National Identity|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=A2SXphY-DvIC&pg=PA133|date=2009-07-27|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-139-48891-4|page=133|access-date=2021-09-20|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112055012/https://books.google.com/books?id=A2SXphY-DvIC&pg=PA133|dead-url=no}}</ref>美國在許多方面都有自己獨特的社會和文化特徵，如[[美國英語|方言]]、[[美國音樂|音樂]]、{{link-en|美國的視覺藝術|Visual art of the United States|藝術}}、[[美國社會|社會習慣]]、[[美國飲食|飲食]]和{{link-en|美國民俗|Folklore of the United States|民俗}}。<ref name="Society in Focus">Thompson, William, and Joseph Hickey (2005). ''Society in Focus''. Boston: Pearson. {{ISBN|0-205-41365-X}}.</ref>
{{clear}}

==對外移民==
[[File:Map of the American Diaspora in the World.svg|thumb|300x300px|美國僑民的分佈（包括美國公民及其子女）<br>
{{Legend|#000000|美國}}
{{Legend|#000070|+ 1,000,000}}
{{Legend|#0404be|+ 100,000}}
{{Legend|#3d7aff|+ 10,000}}
{{Legend|#a7bdf6|+ 1,000}}]]
許多國家或地區都有來自美國的移民，包括阿根廷、澳大利亚、巴西、{{link-en|美國裔加拿大人|American Canadians|加拿大}}、智利、[[在華美國人|中國]]、哥斯大黎加、法國、德國、{{link-en|在香港美國人|Americans in Hong Kong|香港}}、印度、日本、墨西哥、紐西蘭、巴基斯坦、菲律賓、韓國、阿聯酋和[[美國裔英國人|英國]]。{{as of|2016}}，約有900萬美國公民生活在海外。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://travel.state.gov/content/dam/travel/CA_By_the_Numbers.pdf|title=CA by the Numbers|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616233331/https://travel.state.gov/content/dam/travel/CA_By_the_Numbers.pdf|archive-date=2016-06-16}}</ref>
{{clear}}

